Text:
Great compilation there, Ulyana!! Thanks a lot for sharing.....

Well, I'll dig the music when I get it downloaded, but after reading the file list I can say in advance  this is a must have for any jazz collector,  indeed,  any possibility to get the covers as well ?
[img]http://www.fancysplace.com/smileys/c014.gif[/img][img]http://www.fancysplace.com/smileys/c011.gif[/img]

Thank you so much for sharing this set, Ulyana.  I cannot wait to get it all downloaded and to start in on it.

I would be VERY interested in receiving the CD inserts with the complete discographies.  In fact, "VERY" doesn't say it strong enough (I am quite meticulous in the construction of my mp3 library,  and those materials would save me SO much research time with regard to determining recording dates and such).

Thanks again!

P.S.  Any chance that you have Vols. 2 and 3 as well?  Not that I mean to be greedy...;-)

Thanks much! Not able to complete the download but a few tracks have completed.  A really great collection. Would greatly appreciate if someone can re-seed, but if not, I am glad to get the tracks I did.  Leaving the 86.8% available for anyone that wants to get a partial set.
Thanks so much for this compilation! I'm also stuck at 86.8 % so a re-seed from anyone whould be great.
I am also stuck on all 3 volumes - Can you please (please, please) re-seed these? Spasiba Bolshoi!
If  anybody has this, please reseed.  I am also stuck at 86.8%.  I will gladly do the same.
